$lang['The 4 would represent 400 (4×100), 2 would represent 20 (2×10), 3 would represent 3 (3×1), and the 0 would represent 0 (0x0).'] = '4 a yi ta yimela 400 (4×100), 2 a yi ta yimela 20 (2×10), 3 a yi ta yimela 3 (3×1), naswona 0 a yi ta yimela 0 (0x0).';
